<p>I wasn't sure whether to publish this review or not.</p>
<p>One of our members wanted a really simple shopping cart for Drupal. They found the Basic Cart module and asked me about it.</p>
<p>So, I set up and tested Basic Cart. Everything worked great, until the end when I realized there was no payment gateway. None. Basic Cart is a great little e-commerce store ... except it has no way to pay.</p><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/ostrainingdrupal/~4/hO-C1emxLiE" height="1" width="1"/>
